Package cs350s21project.datatype

Class CoordinateWorld

  • java.lang.Object
    • cs350s21project.datatype.CoordinateWorld
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    I_Unitable<CoordinateWorld>, I_XMLable, java.lang.Comparable<CoordinateWorld>
    public class CoordinateWorld
extends java.lang.Object
implements I_Unitable<CoordinateWorld>, I_XMLable
    Defines the basic elements of arbitrary two-dimensional Cartesian coordinate system based on Universal Transverse Mercator (UTM) latitude and longitude.
